          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "3",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "All symmetric resonances were assumed to be p-wave for",
                "this analysis."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "4",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "While there is a slight shape difference between the",
                "transmission profiles for S-wave levels of the two spin",
                "states, it is insufficient to determine the resonance J",
                "values decisively. So 'Spin J' in the data has still",
                "uncertainty, but is consistent with the previous",
                "assignments."
              ]
            }
          ],
